SGGS Web App & Graphics Club

ABOUT US

SGGS Web App & Graphics Club is a student-run organization at SGGSIE&T, dedicated to fostering creativity and innovation in web development and graphic design. Our club provides a platform for students to learn, collaborate, and showcase their skills in these dynamic fields. We organize workshops, hackathons, and design challenges to help members enhance their technical abilities and gain practical experience. Join us to explore the exciting world of web apps and graphics, connect with like-minded individuals, and unleash your creative potential!

RECENT EVENTS

Hackfusion 2.0

We Organized a National Level Hackathon named Hackfusion 2.0. It was a 36 hours hour hackathon with the theme of a popular web series Squid Game. It was a successfull event where coders put their all into developing their unique projects. Hats off to our team working day and night into organizing this successfull grand event.

Flutterflow Workshop

This worshop was totally organized by the female members of our club. In this workshop we called a teacher to teach Flutterflow to the students of our college. At the end of the workshop we also gave the students stickers. It was a successful workshop thanks to the girls team of the club

Android Workshop

We organized a workshop on Android Development. In this workshop we taught the students how to develop an android app using Android Studio. It was a successful event where students learned a lot about Android Development. This was a successful workshop thanks to the hardworking Organizing team.
